| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1641 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fdd00f2d-c1b7-5aed-8084-06f7f1eca1e2"
